Debian / Ubuntu / CentOS 5.x package, for Apache Crowd Connector

More information can be found at http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CROWD/Installing+the+Crowd+Apache+Connector+on+Ubuntu+Linux

To build rpm for CentOS 5.x

tar cvzf mod_authnz_crowd-xxx.tar.gz mod_authnz_crowd-xxx
cd mod_authnz_crowd-xxx.tar.gz {BUILDROOT}/SOURCES
cp mod-authnz-crowd-xxx.spec {BUILDROOT}/SPECS

cd {BUILDROOT}/SPECS
rpmbuild -bb --clean mod-authnz-crowd-xxx.spec
